                    </div>
                    <span>This is a wonderful book on the industry. If you are interested in becoming a contractor and don't have much experience with the all of building aspects, this book should enlighten you. I highly recommend it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great Start</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>4</span>
